{
  "texts": [
    "• SQuAD (Rajpurkar et al, 2016).",
    "The SQuAD dataset is constructed with over 100K samples through crowdsourcing.",
    "Annotators generate questions based on Wikipedia articles, and the answers are derived from corresponding passages in the text.",
    "• SQuAD 2.0 (Rajpurkar et al, 2018).",
    "Built upon the SQuAD dataset, SQuAD 2.0 introduces an additional 53,775 unanswerable questions crafted through crowdsourced reverse engineering."
  ]
}